Titolo: Day One: Garry's Incident

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Day One: Garry's Incident is a PC survival game developed and published by Wild Games Studio in Mascouche, Qu√©bec, Canada and released on 25 September 2013. The game received primarily negative reviews from critics, one of whom was known as TotalBiscuit, publishing his review on YouTube; Wild Games Studio then had the video taken down using the site's automated copyright complaints system. TotalBiscuit then uploaded a response/follow-up video claiming that the copyright complaint was part of a deliberate attempt to censor online criticisms. After receiving negative attention for their copyright complaint, the game's developers apologized and withdrew the complaint. The developers were also accused of astroturfing online reviews on Metacritic.

Genere: First-person shooter

Valutazione: N/A
